111
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,360
Apa kabar?

112
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:40,440
Tak butuh pakaian untuk bahagia, bukan?

113
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,560
Kalian berencana bertemu di sini?

114
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,840
Sama sekali tidak.

115
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:46,800
Aku akan pergi.
