/ Ya.

168
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,440
Kau cantik.

169
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,160
Terima kasih.

170
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:24,160
Jaket kami, tolong.

171
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:28,440
Terima kasih, Samu.

172
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,440
Aku akan pergi.

173
