Jangan, Omar.

174
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,800
Dengarkan.

175
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:47,840
Aku tak bisa tidur.
Lihat betapa telernya aku.

176
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:49,400
Itu masalahmu, Ander.

177
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,880
Jangan cemas, aku akan mengurusnya.

178
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:55,440
Omar!

179
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:59,720
Hei, cobalah sedikit.
Ini asyik sekali. Lihat saja!

180
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:00,760
Kubilang tidak!

181
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,040
Omar, kumohon! Dengarkan aku!

182
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:08,080
Silakan teler sesukamu,
tetapi jangan ganggu aku!

183
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:16,320
Lihat sisi positifnya.

184
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,400
Kita punya lebih.

185
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:21,040
Aku tak mau lagi.

186
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,520
Ander!

187
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:32,720
Patrick.

188
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:33,640
Hati-hati!

189
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:38,600
