190
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,000
Patrick.

191
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,720
Omar!

192
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,440
Omar!

193
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,800
Minggir!

194
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:50,440
Sial!

195
00:14:50,520 --> 00:14:52,000
Patrick!

