215
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:31,920
Permisi. Kami akan tutup.

216
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:37,520
Ayahmu memintaku masuk tim debat.

217
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:39,640
Benarkah?
